Denmark Tells Nationals to Leave Tokyo, Danmarks Radio Says

-- B y   T a s n e e m   B r o g g e r
-- 
2011-03-17T11:18:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-17/denmark-tells-nationals-to-leave-tokyo-danmarks-radio-says.html
  Denmark ’s embassy in  Japan  is
telling all Danish nationals to leave the capital  Tokyo  amid
concern civilians may be exposed to dangerous doses of
radiation, Danmarks Radio reported.   “We’re recommending that Danes leave Tokyo and the area
north of Tokyo or completely leave the country,” said Franz-
Michael S. Mellbin, Denmark’s ambassador to Japan, the
Copenhagen-based broadcaster reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tasneem Brogger at 
 tbrogger@bloomberg.net  